column5:
13 pages, 2 figures; the abstract and introduction are substantially
  revised from the previous version; a mathematical typo is corrected in
  section 4;

This paper has been withdrawn by the authors because it is superseded
  by "R\'enyi Entropy, Signed Probabilities, and the Qubit" by Adam
  Brandenburger, Pierfrancesco La Mura, and Stuart Zoble (arXiv:2010.02111;
  also published in Entropy 2022, 24(10), 1412;
  https://doi.org/10.3390/e24101412)
